      "text": "Irr taws Eenaidneeks iſ-\nſalzis/ tad ehdini wiẍxu ar Mai-\nſi/ un kad wiẍnam flahpst/ tad\ndsirdini winnu ar uhdeni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tu faṙahſi kwehlat-\nnas Ohgles us winna Galwu/\nun tas KUNGS tew to mak-\nfahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Seemeka Wehſch\naſdsenn to Leetu/ un weens du-\nmigß Waigs (nowaja) kas ſlep-\npent plukſchke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Labbaki irr Juinta Kaṙ-\nta dsihiwoht/ neka pee weenas\nRehjejas Seeivas weenâ Nam-\nma koypa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Labba Wehſts' no tahtas\nSemmes/ irr ka aufsts uhdens\nweenai iſflahpuschai Dwehfelet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Taitnajs/ kaṡ kaḣda\nVeṡdeewiga Breekscha lohkahs/\nirr ka ſajukkuſi Akka un famai-\ntahts Awots.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dands Meddu ehft ne irr\nlabbi/ ta ne irr Gohds fawu pa-\n"
